  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Add About Page Navigation Link to Homepage\n\nImplement proper navigation from the homepage \"Dowiedz się więcej\" (Learn more) button to the localized About page.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the \"Dowiedz się więcej\" button component on the homepage\n- Update the button's link/navigation to route to the About page with proper language prefix\n- Ensure the link format follows the pattern: /<lang>/about where <lang> is the current user's language code\n- Preserve the current language context when navigating (e.g., if user is on /pl homepage, button should link to /pl/about)\n- Verify the About page exists for all supported language variants\n- Test navigation works correctly for all language versions of the site\n- Ensure the link is accessible and follows proper routing conventions (use router navigation, not hard-coded hrefs if applicable)",
